reviews.review_text:
It's not slow... In fact, I feel this version, as well as the Hubbard-Bandrofcheck AUD from the night before, are the best uploads of these two Merriweather shows!  My ears tell me they both sound incredible!
Just my opinion, though.
#PlayDead
